'''仰光環狀鐵路'''（{{lang-en|'''Yangon Circular Railway'''}}）是一條位於[[緬甸|緬甸]]最大城市[[仰光|仰光]]的[[通勤鐵路線|通勤鐵路線]]，主要營運於仰光市內以及周邊[[衛星城鎮|衛星城鎮]]。該鐵路由[[緬甸鐵道部|緬甸鐵道部]]營運，環狀鐵路總長約{{convert|45.9|km|mi|sing=on}}，其中包含39座車站，每日運行約20班車，提供販售100,000至150,000張車票。<ref>{{cite journal |url=http://eversion.news-eleven.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=821 |title=Inter-states and regions railroad tracks all heading to Nay Pyi Taw |work=Bi-Weekly Eleven |date=2010-10-15 |volume=3 |issue=30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110714173107/http://eversion.news-eleven.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=821 |archivedate=2011-07-14 |journal= |access-date=2015-03-22 }}</ref><ref name="railway bazzar">{{cite news |url=http://www.irrawaddy.org/multimedia.php?art_id=10074 |title=The Railway Bazaar |date=2008-01-30 |author=Yeni |publisher=The Irrawaddy |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080208202549/http://www.irrawaddy.org/multimedia.php?art_id=10074 |archivedate=2008-02-08 |accessdate=2015-03-22 }}</ref><ref name=uncrd>{{cite paper | url=http://www.uncrd.or.jp/env/3rd-regional-est-forum/doc/23_Myanmar.pdf | title=Third Regional EST Forum: Presentation of Myanmar | publisher=Ministry of Transport, Myanmar | location=Singapore | date=17–19 March 2008 | journal= | access-date=2015-03-22 | archive-date=2009-02-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090226114154/http://www.uncrd.or.jp/env/3rd-regional-est-forum/doc/23_Myanmar.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>環狀線繞行一圈約為三小時，可以覽遍仰光市容。環狀線的車票價格便宜，是低收入的仰光市民重要的交通工具。

環狀線每日自早上3時45分至晚上10時15分營運，順、逆時針方向均有班次行駛，票價計費方式是每15英里收費100[[緬元|緬元]]（約美金9分）。<ref>{{cite journal | url=http://www.news-eleven.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=6561:-rbe-&catid=43:2009-11-10-07-39-09&Itemid=111 | title=13 Coaches from Japan Arrived for Yangon Circular Railway | work=Bi-Weekly Eleven | date=2011-01-04 | language=my | journal= | author= | access-date=2015-03-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110925201535/http://www.news-eleven.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=6561:-rbe-&catid=43:2009-11-10-07-39-09&Itemid=111 | archive-date=2011-09-25 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>非緬甸籍旅客在[[仰光中央車站|仰光中央車站]]可以向服務台購買一日乘車券，價格為1200緬元或1美元。

==歷史==
仰光環狀線於[[英屬緬甸|英國殖民時期]]開始建造<ref>{{cite book|last=Codrington|first=Stephen|title=Planet Geography|url=https://archive.org/details/planetgeography0000codr|publisher=Solid Star Press|date=2005|pages=[https://archive.org/details/planetgeography0000codr/page/568 568]|isbn=9780957981935}}</ref>，並於1954年增建為雙軌系統。<ref>{{cite book|last=Etherton|first=David|author2=Terry Standley |title=Human Settlements Sector Review: Union of Myanmar|publisher=United nations Centre for Human Settlements|date=May 1990|pages=71|isbn=9789211311280|language=en}}</ref>

2011年7月，緬甸鐵道部宣布希望將仰光環狀線的經營民營化，自從政府經營環狀線後，該線每月平均虧損2億6000萬[[緬元|緬元]]，相當於32萬5000美元。而總體收入僅有4200萬緬元，相當於5萬2500美元。<ref name="wkkl">{{cite news|url=http://www.mmtimes.com/2011/business/586/biz58603.html|title=Rail privatisation drive continues|last=Win Ko Ko Latt|author2=Su Hlaing Tun|date=1 August 2011|work=Myanmar Times|accessdate=13 September 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130913183512/http://www.mmtimes.com/2011/business/586/biz58603.html|archivedate=2013年9月13日}}</ref>主要虧損原因來自於相對低廉的乘車票價。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mmtimes.com/2011/business/585/biz58505.html|title=Yangon’s rail network to be privatised|date=25 July 2011|work=Myanmar Times|accessdate=13 September 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130913183447/http://www.mmtimes.com/2011/business/585/biz58505.html|archivedate=2013年9月13日}}</ref>

2012年12月，[[日本|日本]][[國際協力機構|國際協力機構]]向緬甸政府提出{{tsl|en|Yangon City Development Committee|仰光都市發展計畫}}的協助，其中包括改善都市交通的基礎建設。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mmtimes.com/index.php/special-features/162-wheels-2013/5814-waiting-for-the-train-upgrading-the-yangon-circle-line.html?start=1|title=Waiting for the train: upgrading the Yangon circle line|last=Mudditt|first=Jessica|date=25 March 2013|work=Myanmar Times|accessdate=13 September 2013|archive-date=2015-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150403020346/http://www.mmtimes.com/index.php/special-features/162-wheels-2013/5814-waiting-for-the-train-upgrading-the-yangon-circle-line.html?start=1|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==車站==
仰光環狀鐵路沿線擁有39座車站，連接了仰光大部分重要區域。線路起點於[[仰光中央車站|仰光中央車站]]、迄點於[[敏加拉頓車站|敏加拉頓車站]]，是距離[[仰光國際機場|仰光國際機場]]最近的車站。<ref name=minami>{{cite web | url=http://www.minamitours.com/yangon_circular.htm | title=Yangon Circular Railways Schedule | publisher=Minami Tours | accessdate=2009-01-18 | archive-date=2008-07-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080723225823/http://www.minamitours.com/yangon_circular.htm | dead-url=no }}</ref>運行方式：右行（R）為仰光中央車站往東方出發之方向、左行（L）則為往西方。

